"title": "1060: God, greatness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1060: god, greatness of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's nature, deeds and attributes are incomparable, for which he deserves all praise.</p>\n<h2>God is great</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:6\">JER 10:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:25\">1CH 16:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:4\">PSA 96:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11\">1CH 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5\">NEH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:6\">ISA 12:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's name is great</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:23\">EZK 36:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:9\">JOS 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:22\">1SA 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:42\">1KI 8:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:32\">2CH 6:32</a></p>\n<h2>God is a great king</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">PSA 47:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:7\">PSA 47:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:2\">PSA 48:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:14\">MAL 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:35\">MAT 5:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">1TI 6:15</a></p>\n<h2>God's deeds are great</h2>\n<h3>He does great things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:4\">PSA 136:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:7\">JDG 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:9\">ISA 55:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:19\">JER 32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:49\">LUK 1:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:20\">EPH 3:20</a></p>\n<h3>His acts are powerful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:29\">DEU 9:29</a></strong> <em>God's powerful acts are often associated with the exodus.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:7\">EXO 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:261\">DEU 9:261</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:5\">19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:10\">2SA 23:10</a>ISA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam40:26\">40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:17\">JER 32:17</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">NAM 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:19–1:20</a> <em>His great power at work in the resurrection</em></p>\n<h2>God's attributes are great</h2>\n<h3>His great love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:4\">PSA 108:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:19\">NUM 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:8\">2CH 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4\">EPH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>His great mercy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:13\">1CH 21:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:31\">NEH 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:17\">ROM 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>His great anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:13\">2KI 22:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:11\">PSA 90:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:10\">PSA 102:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:5\">JER 21:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:37\">JER 32:37</a></p>\n<h2>God's gifts are great</h2>\n<h3>He bestows great gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:18\">DAN 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:2\">GEN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:25\">1SA 26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:25\">1CH 29:25</a></p>\n<h3>He gives great joy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:43\">NEH 12:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:22\">EZR 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:7\">PSA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:3\">PSA 126:3</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of God's greatness</h2>\n<h3>God's power is known in the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:2\">PSA 126:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:6\">2CH 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:6\">2CH 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:2\">PSA 99:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:3\">DAN 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>People are astonished</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:43\">LUK 9:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5\">HAB 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:26\">LUK 5:26</a></p>\n<h3>God must be praised for his greatness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:1\">PSA 48:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:3\">DEU 32:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:1\">PSA 89:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:4\">PSA 96:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:3\">PSA 145:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's greatness makes him unique</h2>\n<h3>There is no-one like him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:2\">PSA 150:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:22\">2SA 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:19\">PSA 71:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:10\">PSA 86:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:3\">PSA 145:3</a></p>\n<h3>He is greater than other gods</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:11\">EXO 18:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:7\">DEU 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:17\">DEU 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:5\">2CH 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:5\">PSA 135:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:4-1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:4–8:6</a></p>\n<h3>God is greater than human power and pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:12\">JOB 33:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:7-2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:7–32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:7\">ISA 40:6–40:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:20\">1JN 3:20</a></p>",
